<br>
First of all, this is what I wanted.  I needed the criticism from as many people as I could possibly get.  So please, continue your posts along this thread on what went wrong, just please turn your finger where it was meant to go... on me (Don't worry, I can take it ).  I understand where things went wrong, I now understand HOW things went wrong, but more importantly, from this thread, I know how to make things better.  Mid level raids WILL NOT be like this again.  I can assure you of that.  <br>
<br>
